  ALLERGY RELIEF PROTOCOL — Shopify OS 2.0 Section File
  ============================================================
  File: sections/allergy-relief-protocol.liquid
  Paired with: templates/page.allergy-relief-protocol.json

  INSTALLATION:
  1. Upload all 7 .webp files from /assets/ to your Shopify
     theme's Assets folder (Edit code > Assets > Upload file).
  2. Copy this file into your theme's sections/ folder.
  3. Copy page.allergy-relief-protocol.json into templates/.
  4. Go to Online Store > Pages > Add page.
  5. Under "Theme template", select allergy-relief-protocol.
  6. Save. Preview via Themes > three-dot menu > Preview,
     then navigate to /pages/your-page-handle.

